{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id7873f3d4-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s80a–49"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"80a–49"},"text":"§ 80a–49.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Construction with other laws","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Except where specific provision is made to the contrary, nothing in this subchapter shall affect (1) the jurisdiction of the Commission under the Securities Act of 1933 [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s77a"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 77a","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s78a"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 78a","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], the Trust Indenture Act of 1939 ["},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s77aaa"},"text":"15 U.S.C. 77aaa","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], or subchapter II of this chapter, over any person, security, or transaction, or (2) the rights, obligations, duties, or liabilities of any person under such Acts; nor shall anything in this subchapter affect the jurisdiction of any other commission, board, agency, or officer of the United States or of any State or political subdivision of any State, over any person, security, or transaction, insofar as such jurisdiction does not conflict with any provision of this subchapter or of any rule, regulation, or order hereunder."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id7873f3d5-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1940-08-22/ch686"},"text":"Aug. 22, 1940, ch. 686","children":[],"tail":", title I, § 50, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/54/846"},"text":"54 Stat. 846","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/203/tIX/s986/c/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–203, title IX, § 986(c)(4)","children":[],"tail"